Ruwan&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12741077" author="ruwan" created="Sun, 9 Aug 2009 13:04:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has been fixed on the trunk as well as the 1.3 branch and will be available with the 1.3 release, with this issue I also fixed an issue with cloning the faults. SOAPFault shouldn&apos;t be treated as normal OMElements because they are extended from a certain API to provide the fault functionality.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
